His Majesty and Prince Regent
had another row.

25
00:02:05,966 --> 00:02:06,805
His Majesty was furious.

26
00:02:07,046 --> 00:02:09,446
He had Prince Regent copy out
the genealogy a thousand times

27
00:02:09,645 --> 00:02:11,405
before allowing his return
to the imperial court.

28
00:02:13,125 --> 00:02:15,085
After all, His Majesty is the monarch.

29
00:02:15,926 --> 00:02:17,286
Uncle has crossed the line.

30
00:02:18,446 --> 00:02:19,245
Exactly.

31
00:02:20,166 --> 00:02:20,926
Mind your step.

32
00:02:21,135 --> 00:02:27,935
(Ciming Hall)

33
00:02:34,046 --> 00:02:35,886
Are you sure you want to go in,
Your Highness?

34
00:02:36,805 --> 00:02:37,606
Of course.

35
00:03:02,886 --> 00:03:04,365
I find that the servants here

36
00:03:05,125 --> 00:03:06,326
can really take a hint.

37
00:03:07,606 --> 00:03:10,766
You're free to come and go around here.

38
00:03:14,046 --> 00:03:15,326
Concerning our relationship,

39
00:03:15,606 --> 00:03:16,805
they won't stop me.

40
00:03:19,046 --> 00:03:19,726
Why?

41
00:03:20,645 --> 00:03:22,926
Do you want me to climb over the wall

42
00:03:23,286 --> 00:03:24,446
like Yemu Zhen did?

43
00:03:28,006 --> 00:03:30,286
I wonder how I've offended you.

44
00:03:31,685 --> 00:03:33,046
You'd rather drink alone

45
00:03:33,565 --> 00:03:34,766
and play weiqi

46
00:03:35,365 --> 00:03:36,525
than meet me.

47
00:03:40,525 --> 00:03:41,486
I've disgraced myself

48
00:03:42,286 --> 00:03:44,365
for your sake.

49
00:03:46,125 --> 00:03:48,125
Do you insist on giving me
the cold shoulder?

50
00:03:54,926 --> 00:03:55,685
Why?

51
00:03:57,166 --> 00:03:59,006
Just because I used Zhuohua,

52
00:04:00,206 --> 00:04:01,685
you ice me out like this.

53
00:04:02,486 --> 00:04:03,886
Does she hold more importance than I do

54
00:04:04,645 --> 00:04:05,926
in your heart?

55
00:04:11,245 --> 00:04:12,645
Do you really mean what you said?

56
00:04:14,645 --> 00:04:16,046
I have a question.

57
00:04:17,406 --> 00:04:19,846
On your road towards the throne,

58
00:04:21,445 --> 00:04:23,365
to what extent will you do?

59
00:04:24,765 --> 00:04:25,726
To slay the dragon,

60
00:04:27,526 --> 00:04:29,805
I have to sacrifice some of my pawns.

61
00:04:31,646 --> 00:04:34,565
Everything that has been done
is for the final result.

62
00:04:40,486 --> 00:04:43,046
It's time to wrap up the game.

63
00:04:44,846 --> 00:04:47,365
However, there's one more thing
we need to fight for.

64
00:04:48,885 --> 00:04:50,685
I wonder if you're interested

65
00:04:51,685 --> 00:04:53,765
in finishing this game with me.

66
00:04:54,606 --> 00:04:55,486
You should know

67
00:04:57,005 --> 00:04:59,286
that I'm always standing toe to toe
against those noble families.

68
00:05:00,565 --> 00:05:02,325
I'm afraid you can't afford to lose help
from the Zhou family

69
00:05:02,885 --> 00:05:04,086
in this game.

70
00:05:05,885 --> 00:05:06,805
Therefore,

71
00:05:08,685 --> 00:05:09,805
I'm not in for this.

72
00:05:10,966 --> 00:05:12,286
Why do you care about
those noble families?

73
00:05:15,885 --> 00:05:17,805
We do all this for our great endeavor.

74
00:05:18,166 --> 00:05:19,286
When this is over,

75
00:05:19,445 --> 00:05:21,406
I'll remove them one by one.

76
00:05:44,606 --> 00:05:46,086
Sooner or later, you will know

77
00:05:47,846 --> 00:05:49,565
I made the right choice.

78
00:06:04,125 --> 00:06:05,046
(Official Zhou.)

79
00:06:05,565 --> 00:06:07,166
Are you positive about what you said?

80
00:06:07,885 --> 00:06:08,966
You said that once the plan succeeds,

81
00:06:09,286 --> 00:06:10,486
the Talent Appreciation System
will be replaced

82
00:06:11,245 --> 00:06:14,325
by the perpetual heritability.

83
00:06:14,846 --> 00:06:15,805
Certainly.

84
00:06:21,286 --> 00:06:22,086
Your Highness.

85
00:06:24,445 --> 00:06:26,926
I understand that you don't have
complete trust in me now.

86
00:06:27,486 --> 00:06:28,526
Today,

87
00:06:29,166 --> 00:06:31,245
I'll give you all a gift.

88
00:06:33,365 --> 00:06:34,646
Turn in these missives

89
00:06:35,685 --> 00:06:38,125
during the morning assembly tomorrow.

90
00:06:39,445 --> 00:06:42,726
The biggest obstacle
to your prosperous life

91
00:06:43,526 --> 00:06:45,205
will then be crushed.

92
00:06:49,445 --> 00:06:50,765
Is this feasible?

93
00:06:52,765 --> 00:06:55,765
These may not be enough,
Your Highness.

94
00:06:59,365 --> 00:07:01,846
Read this and see if it's enough,
Official Zhou.

95
00:07:06,046 --> 00:07:07,046
On this day,

96
00:07:07,486 --> 00:07:09,926
the late Emperor passed away.

97
00:07:31,526 --> 00:07:32,885
Why are you coughing again?

98
00:07:38,325 --> 00:07:42,046
Perhaps it gets worse
after the row with His Majesty.

99
00:07:45,685 --> 00:07:47,966
After all, His Majesty
is in a different position now.

100
00:07:48,646 --> 00:07:50,646
He has his own perspective and concerns.

101
00:07:52,166 --> 00:07:53,926
You should try another way
to talk to him.

102
00:07:58,046 --> 00:07:59,086
Besides,

103
00:07:59,486 --> 00:08:01,125
he has been under great duress recently

104
00:08:01,885 --> 00:08:03,005
and become grouchy.

105
00:08:03,565 --> 00:08:04,885
That was why he quarreled roundly
with you.

106
00:08:15,365 --> 00:08:16,365
However,

107
00:08:16,606 --> 00:08:18,086
I think the punishment he gave
is a good one.

108
00:08:18,805 --> 00:08:19,805
During these days,

109
00:08:20,086 --> 00:08:22,606
you can copy the genealogy at home

110
00:08:23,046 --> 00:08:24,005
and take a good rest.

111
00:08:24,005 --> 00:08:24,526
You haven't rested

112
00:08:24,526 --> 00:08:25,846
since returning

113
00:08:25,966 --> 00:08:28,646
and your body doesn't recover well.

114
00:08:36,166 --> 00:08:36,926
Zhuohua.

115
00:08:40,485 --> 00:08:42,565
If one day I'm gone,

116
00:08:44,166 --> 00:08:45,286
what will you do?

117
00:08:47,926 --> 00:08:50,605
I'll find a young and handsome man

118
00:08:50,926 --> 00:08:53,246
and take him to your tomb every day

119
00:08:53,445 --> 00:08:55,406
to show you how lovable I am.

120
00:09:00,845 --> 00:09:02,366
What a unique turn of mind

121
00:09:02,526 --> 00:09:04,965
you have.

122
00:09:06,085 --> 00:09:07,325
I shall see

123
00:09:07,965 --> 00:09:09,926
who have the guts to visit my tomb

124
00:09:10,286 --> 00:09:11,685
with you.

125
00:09:13,565 --> 00:09:15,845
If you're worried
that I can't find a brave man,

126
00:09:16,246 --> 00:09:18,205
you'd better stay well

127
00:09:18,246 --> 00:09:20,485
and accompany me for a long time.

128
00:09:28,485 --> 00:09:30,286
You still have a wonderful life ahead.

129
00:09:32,766 --> 00:09:33,926
You must live on well

130
00:09:35,565 --> 00:09:37,445
even without me.

131
00:09:39,685 --> 00:09:41,845
Why are you saying all this to me
all of a sudden?

132
00:09:46,445 --> 00:09:47,725
I just feel

133
00:09:49,646 --> 00:09:51,166
that my body

134
00:09:51,485 --> 00:09:53,126
is somewhat weak.

135
00:09:54,766 --> 00:09:57,046
All the more reason you should

136
00:09:57,406 --> 00:09:59,006
take good care of your health.

137
00:10:02,006 --> 00:10:02,685
I will.

138
00:10:07,835 --> 00:10:09,406
(Xuanzheng Hall)

139
00:10:09,406 --> 00:10:10,485
