140
00:10:10,725 --> 00:10:11,965
if you have nothing else to report,

141
00:10:12,445 --> 00:10:14,205
we should call it a day.

142
00:10:15,845 --> 00:10:17,886
I have something to report,
Your Majesty.

143
00:10:18,725 --> 00:10:21,286
I want to accuse Prince Regent
of amassing military power

144
00:10:21,406 --> 00:10:22,766
and disrespecting the monarch.

145
00:10:24,046 --> 00:10:24,766
Your Majesty.

146
00:10:25,126 --> 00:10:26,605
I have something to report too.

147
00:10:27,166 --> 00:10:30,526
I want to accuse Prince Regent
of launching carnage

148
00:10:30,845 --> 00:10:32,605
and abducting lady folks.

149
00:10:33,766 --> 00:10:36,126
I have something to report,
Your Majesty.

150
00:10:36,445 --> 00:10:38,685
I want to accuse Prince Regent
of embezzling military funds.

151
00:10:39,526 --> 00:10:41,085
I have something to report,
Your Majesty.

152
00:10:41,565 --> 00:10:43,246
I have something to report,
Your Majesty.

153
00:10:52,526 --> 00:10:53,766
Something's looming over.

154
00:11:00,166 --> 00:11:02,286
Did she bring an umbrella?

155
00:11:06,286 --> 00:11:07,766
Amassed military power,

156
00:11:08,366 --> 00:11:09,926
deployed army without permission,

157
00:11:10,485 --> 00:11:12,126
launched carnage,

158
00:11:12,325 --> 00:11:14,926
pillaged people and military funds,

159
00:11:15,286 --> 00:11:17,246
defied the monarch,
and plotted a treason.

160
00:11:19,406 --> 00:11:20,445
Prince Regent.

161
00:11:21,646 --> 00:11:23,325
Very well done.

162
00:11:31,085 --> 00:11:31,766
Your Majesty.

163
00:11:32,085 --> 00:11:34,965
The seven condemnations
are merely an allegation.

164
00:11:35,445 --> 00:11:36,685
They presented the evidence,

165
00:11:36,845 --> 00:11:38,205
however,
their accusations are conflicting

166
00:11:38,205 --> 00:11:39,166
and flawed.

167
00:11:39,886 --> 00:11:41,286
Please investigate this thoroughly,
Your Majesty.

168
00:11:41,366 --> 00:11:43,006
Please uphold justice for Prince Regent.

169
00:11:43,845 --> 00:11:46,926
I have something to report,
Your Majesty.

170
00:11:53,445 --> 00:11:54,485
I'm presenting

171
00:11:54,766 --> 00:11:57,565
the ingress record of the palace gate
on the day of the late Emperor's death.

172
00:11:58,485 --> 00:12:01,406
Before the late Emperor's passing,

173
00:12:01,685 --> 00:12:03,886
Prince Regent sought an audience
with the Grand Dowager Empress

174
00:12:04,485 --> 00:12:06,406
and he deployed the army
without permission.

175
00:12:07,406 --> 00:12:09,725
Afterward, someone falsified
the ingress record.

176
00:12:10,565 --> 00:12:11,325
This is blatant proof

177
00:12:11,685 --> 00:12:14,286
of Prince Regent's sinister intention.

178
00:12:14,766 --> 00:12:17,725
I'm afraid the truth
behind the late Emperor's death

179
00:12:18,046 --> 00:12:20,526
has something to do with him too.

180
00:12:21,406 --> 00:12:22,526
I've spared no effort

181
00:12:22,685 --> 00:12:24,565
to obtain this record.

182
00:12:25,085 --> 00:12:28,406
Thanks to my nephew, the chief commander
of the imperial guards.

183
00:12:28,565 --> 00:12:29,766
He is scrupulous enough

184
00:12:30,126 --> 00:12:32,006
and is able to bring the truth to light.

185
00:12:33,526 --> 00:12:36,406
Your Majesty, Prince Regent's action

186
00:12:36,406 --> 00:12:37,445
is very likely to be treason.

187
00:12:37,725 --> 00:12:39,406
Please punish him heavily, Your Majesty.

188
00:12:39,766 --> 00:12:41,965
Please punish him heavily, Your Majesty.

189
00:12:42,366 --> 00:12:45,325
Your Majesty, Prince Regent
is loyal to the country.

190
00:12:45,605 --> 00:12:47,406
He'd never commit
to such a heinous conduct.

191
00:12:48,046 --> 00:12:48,845
I suggest

192
00:12:49,166 --> 00:12:50,166
we should find the person

193
00:12:50,205 --> 00:12:52,366
who falsified the ingress record
of the palace gate.

194
00:12:52,845 --> 00:12:54,646
I fear someone's sabotaging

195
00:12:54,965 --> 00:12:57,006
because of their ulterior motive.

196
00:12:57,485 --> 00:12:58,286
Official Mu.

197
00:12:59,485 --> 00:13:02,166
Everyone knows the relationship
between Prince Regent and you.

198
00:13:02,565 --> 00:13:04,366
Needless to say, you defend him.

199
00:13:04,565 --> 00:13:06,965
However,
we have the conclusive proof here.

200
00:13:07,485 --> 00:13:10,126
Why would Prince Regent
falsify the ingress record

201
00:13:10,126 --> 00:13:12,046
if he had done nothing wrong?

202
00:13:12,166 --> 00:13:14,166
And why is only his name removed

203
00:13:14,166 --> 00:13:16,085
from the falsified record?

204
00:13:17,085 --> 00:13:17,805
Your Majesty...

205
00:13:18,006 --> 00:13:18,766
Enough!

206
00:13:20,845 --> 00:13:23,565
Please simmer down, Your Majesty.

207
00:13:24,485 --> 00:13:26,526
Prince Regent is sacrilegious

208
00:13:26,845 --> 00:13:28,126
and shall not be forgiven.

209
00:13:29,166 --> 00:13:31,445
Have the imperial guards imprison him

210
00:13:32,406 --> 00:13:33,366
for interrogation.

211
00:13:35,565 --> 00:13:36,605
Court adjourned.

212
00:13:36,605 --> 00:13:37,725
Your Majesty!

213
00:13:38,325 --> 00:13:39,085
Your Majesty!

214
00:14:07,805 --> 00:14:08,845
Who let you in?

215
00:14:09,286 --> 00:14:10,646
This is the Prince Regent's residence.

216
00:14:10,845 --> 00:14:12,886
We know exactly where we are.

217
00:14:13,085 --> 00:14:14,725
Under the imperial edict,

218
00:14:15,006 --> 00:14:17,485
we're here to arrest the traitor,
Liu Yan.

219
00:14:18,166 --> 00:14:19,205
Who do you call a traitor?

220
00:14:20,886 --> 00:14:22,166
Prince Regent, for sure.

221
00:14:22,166 --> 00:14:22,805
How dare you?

222
00:14:23,166 --> 00:14:23,845
Stop.

223
00:14:31,766 --> 00:14:32,926
Greetings, Prince Regent.

224
00:14:36,485 --> 00:14:39,366
Prince Regent committed

225
00:14:39,485 --> 00:14:40,445
a heinous crime.

226
00:14:40,685 --> 00:14:42,046
Under the imperial edict,

227
00:14:42,286 --> 00:14:44,725
we'll incarcerate you in the dungeon

228
00:14:45,006 --> 00:14:46,006
until a verdict is delivered.

229
00:14:46,965 --> 00:14:47,685
My Lord.

230
00:14:48,366 --> 00:14:49,205
You can't go with them.

231
00:14:49,886 --> 00:14:50,565
Your Lordship.

232
00:14:51,085 --> 00:14:52,725
This is an imperial edict.

233
00:14:53,246 --> 00:14:55,366
Do you want to defy?

234
00:14:56,685 --> 00:14:58,445
I'm afraid things
could turn ugly for you

235
00:14:58,766 --> 00:15:00,886
if our hands are forced.

236
00:15:01,406 --> 00:15:03,166
Since this is an imperial edict,

237
00:15:03,646 --> 00:15:05,605
I'll obey it.

238
00:15:05,886 --> 00:15:06,565
No, My Lord.

239
00:15:06,685 --> 00:15:07,366
No, My Lord.

240
00:15:07,725 --> 00:15:10,246
Please, Your Lordship.

241
00:15:12,445 --> 00:15:13,085
My Lord.

242
00:15:23,485 --> 00:15:24,325
Where's His Lordship?

243
00:15:24,560 --> 00:15:25,226
He was taken
to the Court of Judicial Review

244
00:15:25,226 --> 00:15:25,960
by the imperial guards.

245
00:15:26,766 --> 00:15:28,085
I would've fought them

246
00:15:28,286 --> 00:15:29,725
if His Lordship didn't stop me.

247
00:15:29,965 --> 00:15:31,006
His Lordship was right.

248
00:15:31,246 --> 00:15:32,166
At this pivotal moment,

249
00:15:32,166 --> 00:15:33,565
we must remain composed.

250
00:15:34,085 --> 00:15:35,565
But His Lordship is under arrest now.

251
00:15:35,886 --> 00:15:37,526
This is a humiliation.

252
00:15:38,286 --> 00:15:40,805
We must help His Lordship
clear his name.

253
00:16:02,766 --> 00:16:03,646
Grandaunt.

254
00:16:05,325 --> 00:16:06,166
Look.

255
00:16:07,366 --> 00:16:08,886
Something is looming over

256
00:16:10,166 --> 00:16:11,246
the Southern Chen, finally.

257
00:16:12,286 --> 00:16:13,205
Jiao.

258
00:16:15,085 --> 00:16:18,166
You can still turn back
before it's too late.

259
00:16:25,286 --> 00:16:27,006
Do you say this
because you care for me?

260
00:16:27,565 --> 00:16:29,406
Why don't you give me
the Evil-erasing Sword?

261
00:16:31,006 --> 00:16:32,605
With its help,

262
00:16:33,565 --> 00:16:36,246
no one will be in my way.

263
00:16:59,485 --> 00:17:00,526
It's fine.

264
00:17:03,046 --> 00:17:04,005
Grandaunt.

265
00:17:06,005 --> 00:17:09,285
You're my dearest family in this world.

266
00:17:10,886 --> 00:17:12,326
I won't hurt you.

267
00:17:13,886 --> 00:17:15,406
I'll have ways and means

268
00:17:17,045 --> 00:17:18,445
to forge my way to the throne

269
00:17:20,245 --> 00:17:21,806
even without the Evil-erasing Sword.

270
00:17:28,926 --> 00:17:29,606
Your Majesty.

271
00:17:30,606 --> 00:17:33,005
Each and every accusation
against Lord Ding

272
00:17:33,285 --> 00:17:34,685
is supported by conclusive evidence.

273
00:17:35,205 --> 00:17:36,126
In my humble opinion,

274
00:17:36,485 --> 00:17:39,005
he should be stripped of his title
